# Project-scoped ignore, overriding the repository-root .vercelignore.
#
# The root file strips package.json, pnpm-lock.yaml and pnpm-workspace.yaml so the
# frontend builds standalone. This project needs them: it is a workspace package whose
# dependency (@beckwithbarrow/cms-client) resolves through the pnpm workspace, and
# without those manifests the function has no dependency tree and every invocation
# fails with FUNCTION_INVOCATION_FAILED before any handler runs.
#
# Keep only genuinely irrelevant things out.
*.log
